data.description: Introducing a remarkable single-family house that ticks all the boxes for convenient living, modern design, and utmost safety. This outstanding property is perfectly situated in a desirable location, offering easy access to tons of amenities, schools, and restaurants! Less than 5 mins from Farmer Joe's, & Cape Christian, which has a huge park for kids of all ages, & basketball court! Upon entering, you'll be greeted by the volume ceilings, which create an immediate sense of space and openness. The ample natural light floods the interior, enhancing the overall ambiance of the home. The well-thought-out floor plan seamlessly connects the various living areas, allowing for effortless entertaining and comfortable family living. The thoughtfully chosen tile flooring adds elegance and easy maintenance throughout the property. Some of the standout features of this property is the NEW ROOF & A/C system, ensuring that you and your loved ones will stay comfortable year-round. The new HURRICANE IMPACT Windows provide an added layer of protection, offering peace of mind during storm seasons, & enhancing the energy efficiency of the home! Small water assessment balance remaining. Flood zone X!
